window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>How can something so wrong be so perfect at the same time? </p> <p>Rule number five: I'm going to show you some things that you'll never forget. </p> <p>It's wrong. Not just this, but everything. I knew it was wrong, but I thought I could get away with it. Why, though? I'm not like this. I'm good. I'm the good girl, the girl with perfect grades, the girl who does everything right, prim, and proper. I don't cause trouble, I don't get into trouble, I don't.... </p> <p>It's only a few days, right? That's what I thought when Ethan and I started our stepbrother with benefits situation. Apparently a few days can be a long time. A few days can change your entire life. </p>"; 
